{% set title = 'LTO Network - Use case - V-ID' %}
{% set description = 'Validation-as-a-service (VaaS)' %}

{% extends "base.njk" %}

{% block content %}

<div class="section-container">
  <section class="hero is-medium" style="background-image: url(/assets/slider-image-car@3x.png);">
    <div class="hero-body">
      <div class="container">
          <div class=""><span class="tag is-rounded is-medium blue-grey"> INTEGRATOR </span></div>
        <h1 class="primary-text">Validation-as-a-service (VaaS)</h1>
          <h2 class="dark-indigo">V-ID certifies, secures and validates all Digital Assets with LTO Network.</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="section-container cutout-top">
  <section class="section secondary no-padding">
    <div class="promo-numbers c">
      <div class="container use-cases">
        <div class="item use-cases">
            <p class="promo-head use-cases">Client</p>
            <img class="promo-client" src="/assets/use-cases/v-id@2x.png">
        </div>
        <div class="item use-cases">
            <p class="promo-head use-cases">Involved parties</p>
          <p class="promo-desc use-cases muted">V-ID has 30+ enterprise clients and 10.000 users who rely on certified, secured and validated digital assets, in whatever form.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="section-container cutin-top-alt cutout-bottom">
    <section class="section">

  <div class="advantages-div">
    <div class="advantages-title-container container">
      <h2 class="deep-lavender">Integrator overview</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="advantages-content-container">

      <div class="columns advantages">
        <div class="column advantages image left-side">
          <div class="advantages left-side column-subdiv">
            <img src="/assets/rocks/rock-1.svg" class="rock-tree">
            <img id="advantages-small-rock-1" src="/assets/small-rock-1.svg">
            <img id="advantages-small-rock-2" src="/assets/small-rock-2.svg">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column advantages is-two-thirds right-side">
          <div class="advantages-text-container right-side">
            <h3 class="title dark-indigo advantages">The problem</h3>
              <div class="content">
            <p class="muted">The core challenge of validation is: How can you know that the file you are verifying was validated by the actual rightful person or entity that represents the publishing organisation? Or in other words, how can you be sure that digital files are not fakes?</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="columns advantages">
        <div class="column advantages image left-side">
          <div class="advantages left-side column-subdiv">
            <img src="/assets/rocks/rock-2.svg" class="rock-rocket">
            <img id="advantages-small-rock-3" src="/assets/small-rock-3.svg">
            <img id="advantages-small-rock-4" src="/assets/small-rock-4.svg">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column advantages is-two-thirds right-side">
          <div class="advantages-text-container right-side">
            <h3 class="title dark-indigo advantages">Solution</h3>
              <div class="content">
                  <p class="muted"> V-ID is a service that detects any unlawful manipulation of any digital file. In order to make files verifiable, they must be validated. V-ID’s validation process involves extracting the fingerprints of files and saving them on the blockchain.</p>
                  <p class="muted">If a file is changed with just one byte, pixel, character or anything else, the fingerprint is changed and V-ID will not be able to verify it. It is crucial to have a secure validation method, because the key to confirm the authenticity of a file is to know the source.</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>


    </div>

    <table class="table advantages has-margin-top-40">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th class="table-icon"></td>
          <th class="dark-indigo" colspan="2">Theme</th>
          <th class="dark-indigo" colspan="2">LTO Network solution</th>
          <th class="dark-indigo" colspan="2">Traditional solution</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>

      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <th class="table-icon"></td>
          <th class="deep-lavender">Data security</th>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-checkmark" src="/assets/table icon - good.svg"> </td>
          <td class="steel">The end-product, often a document, gets hashed by a validated party, and anchored on the LTO Network blockchain.</td>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-x" src="/assets/table icon - bad.svg"></td>
          <td class="steel">With professional PDF-hackers around, certainty on signed documents cant be guaranteed.</td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
          <th class="table-icon"></td>
          <th class="deep-lavender">Data verification</th>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-checkmark" src="/assets/table icon - good.svg"> </td>
          <td class="steel">Through the V-ID, third parties can independently check for authenticity.</td>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-x" src="/assets/table icon - bad.svg"></td>
          <td class="steel">As a third party, checking the originality of a data object with the counterparty is a time-consuming affair.</td>
        </tr>


        <tr>
          <th class="table-icon"></td>
          <th class="deep-lavender">Costs / Speed of anchoring</th>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-checkmark" src="/assets/table icon - good.svg"> </td>
          <td class="steel">LTO’s blockchain is optimized for anchoring, making transactions near-instant and affordable.</td>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-x" src="/assets/table icon - bad.svg"></td>
          <td class="steel">Traditional blockchains tend to be very slow and expensive to anchor this many transactions.</td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
        </tr>
      </tbody>

    </table>

    <div class="btn-container has-text-centered">
    <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Zs17a4cDcU4" class="button is-primary" target="blank">
      Learn more
    </a>
</div>
  </div>
</section>
</div>

